  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 200°C (400°F).",
    "Rinse the prawns and pat them dry with paper towels.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the olive oil, honey, lemon juice, salt, and pepper.",
    "Add the diced American roast to the bowl and toss to coat.",
    "Place the prawns on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Drizzle the American glaze over the prawns and roast in the oven for 8-10 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "Remove the prawns from the oven and garnish with chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
